171
00:09:16,088 --> 00:09:20,593
{\an8}<i>Nagase is now working
by himself as a radio personality.</i>

172
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:21,661
{\an8}REN NAGASE (20)

173
00:09:22,261 --> 00:09:23,496
