184
00:09:49,989 --> 00:09:51,090
I see.

185
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:52,592
{\an8}<i>REN NAGASE'S RADIO GARDEN</i>

186
00:09:52,658 --> 00:09:55,761
{\an8}Good evening!
I'm Ren Nagase from King & Prince.

187
00:09:55,828 --> 00:09:58,965
Well then, let's see.

188
00:09:59,031 --> 00:10:04,937
<i>Nagase wanted to make this show a place
where he can honestly express his feelings</i>

189
00:10:05,004 --> 00:10:08,107
<i>without putting up any facade as an idol.</i>

190
00:10:09,475 --> 00:10:12,078
Our very first theme is,

191
00:10:12,144 --> 00:10:15,848
"What is the most popular
girl's school club right now?"

192
00:10:15,915 --> 00:10:17,283
Let's start with fifth.

193
00:10:17,350 --> 00:10:18,651
Here it is.

194
00:10:19,752 --> 00:10:21,287
I see!

195
00:10:21,354 --> 00:10:23,189
