205
00:10:51,517 --> 00:10:53,486
I like butts better, though.

206
00:10:53,552 --> 00:10:55,354
I prefer large butts.

207
00:10:56,155 --> 00:10:57,823
-Let's move on.
-Fourth place?

208
00:10:57,890 --> 00:10:59,759
I was told to stop, sorry.

209
00:10:59,825 --> 00:11:01,127
"Sha-la-la Hajikeru Love."

210
00:11:01,193 --> 00:11:02,061
<i>Then...</i>

211
00:11:02,328 --> 00:11:04,130
<i>he made one request to the staff.</i>

212
00:11:04,764 --> 00:11:07,500
