229
00:11:43,002 --> 00:11:45,204
<i>Each of them are polishing their acts</i>

230
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:49,475
<i>because they want to
strengthen King & Prince.</i>

231
00:11:52,144 --> 00:11:54,947
