236
00:12:05,891 --> 00:12:08,928
and are successful on our own,
but when we come together,

237
00:12:08,994 --> 00:12:10,429
we're very powerful.

238
00:12:10,763 --> 00:12:12,264
I hope we can be like that.

239
00:12:14,934 --> 00:12:19,171
<i>There is one more member
whom they hold dear.</i>

240
00:12:21,941 --> 00:12:25,911
